{"tid":1933801,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林士街停車場男子高處墮下亡","createTime":"2020-03-19T13:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T20:32:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"783e3563e08de80682ff136d8d37b19946cfbf74","tid":1933801,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"上環林士街多層停車場，今晚(19日)8時許，一名男子懷疑從上址高處墮下，倒臥在現場對開近干諾道中一段行人路，頭爆肢折重傷昏迷，有途人發現報警求助。警員及救護員接報趕至，經初步檢驗，證實男子已傷重死亡，遂取來帳篷遮蓋屍體。警方事後圍封現場，正進一步調查男子身份及其死因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200319/bkn-20200319204222525-0319_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200319%2Fbkn-20200319204222525-0319_00822_001.html&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4fb204d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200319/bkn-20200319204222525-0319_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b9247aedabf0d789e73bbe0aa82fab846007f846","tid":1933801,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185b703cee269f224668efb0c2d0fa00ffc3287a","tid":1933801,"uid":57221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母信唔信？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"64f2e9a108a14e6579ce22d67d446aa7d31aaa9d","tid":1933801,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad13cea113f8efbeaef0c5f9f753c020b40d384","tid":1933801,"uid":2377